Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很危險 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,突破各種艱難的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位年輕有為的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,成為守護這顆星球的緋紅守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一人 結人皇上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,另一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧卡門上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在令人值得紀念的出關儀式前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,兩名備受注目的怪伐軍\N即將展現他們的實力…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的話…太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,來真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 認輸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有機可趁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(鬧鐘)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,(入伍儀式開始時間緊迫)\N(動作快)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,(危險區域 禁止進入)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是今天加入緋紅守護者的\N那歧卡門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是這個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下則報導
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,(備受注目 第567屆新隊員)\N今天即將舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,(備受注目 第567屆新隊員)\N本年度怪伐軍入伍儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,加入怪伐軍的均是通過\N嚴苛SAS適性測試的菁英們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在此介紹今年的候選明星隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要介紹我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(輝煌的家世 志願入怪伐軍)\N結人皇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,現今新日向國評議會議長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-條皇先生的兒子\N-果然是介紹你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,(條皇 評議會議長)\N沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,(條皇 評議會議長)\N其祖先是建國之父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,輝煌家族的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(界人皇 怪伐軍本部長)\N其兄長界人煌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是新日向怪伐軍的本部長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他放棄從政 投身到前線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,另外還有個令人在意的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,根據相關人士的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說結人的超腦力適性較低
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,養尊處優的少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是否能耐得住與怪異艱辛的戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-感覺好差\N-下則報導
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,結人 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腦力值較低 是事實嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不管誰說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,從今天起你就是怪伐軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你 都是為了這天而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以絕對沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,當上怪伐軍\N是你從小夢寐以求的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你可要銘記在心喔 結人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(警報)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怪異警報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然在歡天喜慶的日子攪局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,發布怪異警報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,各地的確切出現機率如下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一擊消滅怪異的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,榮獲七劍星一等勳章的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(卡連崔佛斯少將 超腦力：噬腦者)\N噬腦者 卡蓮崔佛斯少將
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是詩賓少將
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,(吹雪詩賓少將 超腦力：冷卻)\N他凍結了怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,吹雪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也得像他們那樣戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你要…活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,《緋紅結繫》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,現實的Crimｅ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For Heaven's sake
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,接受虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆的幻想 層層逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,絕非完美 I get sick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,轉身而來的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在這瞬息世界中 落下了奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit the venom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 絕頂的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Criminal gets life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been in love
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我何時開始厭倦了這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday I won't be crying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不再傷害 而犧牲了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(緋紅的超腦力)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真幸運 這樣就不算遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是在等卡蓮隊長他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原來同期裡有這麼可愛的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,直見蘭德爾 直見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,旁邊的是妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她們的年紀相同耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是雙胞胎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她在看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,姊姊 不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便露出破綻\N很容易被那種人纏上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,重 妳總是把我當小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我看的是旁邊那位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,界人皇本部長的訓示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,全體 起立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的哥哥耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,擁有高潔志向之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,才能被選進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我為各位的勇氣及熱情\N由衷地感到敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然而在這頻繁受到\N怪異威脅的國家中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天生擁有優秀超腦力之人的招募組
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,及藉由鍛鍊提升腦力的志願組
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力)\N不分彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如不結合各自的腦力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,便無法越過重重難關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,現如今只知道\N怪異來自平流層的斷絕之帶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其他仍有許多未解之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 擁有對付怪異能力的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正是防禦的重要基石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在執行任務的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也別忘了今日心中的抱負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,從此刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,共2168的諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,便是新日向國怪伐軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,緋紅守護者的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(那歧 卡門)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,(結人 皇)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想跟直見搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被人救的時候 你幾歲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,五歲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,當時在怪伐軍裡的女性…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,直見蘭德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然在找這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,名門貴族蘭德爾家的長女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在她身邊的是妹妹 重蘭德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,重小時候 雙親被怪異所殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,之後被蘭德爾家收養
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,與同年齡的直見成為姊妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,12歲時被招募進怪伐軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是訓練時期的榜首
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,直見是第五名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她們是菁英姐妹花嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,重 蘭德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭德爾家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得在父親的就職慶祝會上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好像沒看到救你的人的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不過結人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我得先說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你追重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然她看起來很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而我追直見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 重還是沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因為今天早上妳說\N又做了"紅色繫線之夢"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,別放開…別解開紅色繫線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,跟妳的超腦力有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個 我更擔心姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是否能編列在同一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,姊姊個性較笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得保護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,重 妳好過分喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還是不知道究竟是誰救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟連大哥都不知道是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,結人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們分到同一隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,花火 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,花火一條
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他是那歧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,受訓時期都沒碰到面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我是招募組
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎加入賽特小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,(賽特鳴神大尉)\N我是賽特鳴神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力：放電)\N從今天起就是你們的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如你們所知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,從今天起我們就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggle Arms System 簡稱SAS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,互相共享超腦力一同戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,請新成員自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,順帶一提 我的超腦力是放電
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(花火一條少尉)\N我是花火一條
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力：點火)\N超腦力是點火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,(那歧卡門上等兵)\N我是那歧卡門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力：空氣操作)\N超腦力是空氣操作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,加入怪伐軍是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,(結人皇上等兵)\N我是結人皇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力：念力)\N超腦力是念力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候 曾被怪伐軍救過一命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡我所能的報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,現任隊員也自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,鶇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(鶇娜札中尉)\N我是鶇娜札
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力：透視)\N超腦力是透視
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…我的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,透視很難表現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是鼎鼎大名的結人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,早上都在報導你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,說皇家小少爺要入伍的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,陽炎 你也快自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(陽炎丹伍長)\N第567屆的菜鳥們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力：透明化)\N我是陽炎丹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,遲到的天才 指的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是你自稱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的隊長 正經八百的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,朱雀區域上空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,確認有出現怪異的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,賽特小隊 鏡花小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,提升警戒程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,隊員們立即前往現場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜前往避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,對怪異高射炮 已排除85%的怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其餘仍在下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 我還沒自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,(渡弗雷澤少尉)\N我是渡弗雷澤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力：精神感應)\N超腦力是精神感應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,簡單來說就是心電感應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我會在本部後方支援各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,賽特小隊到E點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,鏡花小隊到F點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對付怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是賽特小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,已確認目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好 讓他們見識見識\N緋紅守護者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧 結人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在後方待機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等待支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,剛入伍的第一天就急著送死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你們今天參觀就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,對喔 我們是志願組
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,解決兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,鏡花小隊 抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,各自移動到戰鬥地點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,重 好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧有姊姊的輔助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,重好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(警告)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找人過來支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不要露出高興的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我根本不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,說了要你們等待支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,來不及的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們兩人去救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧 你太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,重 接著又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要成為幫助人類的怪伐軍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如同那人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-那歧\N-別管我 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-痛…\N-你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧 怪異要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(直見蘭德爾少尉)\N(超腦力：預知未來)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(重蘭德爾少尉)\N(超腦力：念力)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,入伍當天就想死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,壓碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是直見救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因今天剛入伍的\N皇上等兵活躍表現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怪異順利被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,皇上等兵 獲得漂亮的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(嵐詩賓大尉 超腦力：超高速)\N採訪到此為止囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是嵐詩賓大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,詩賓大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,請問今天的戰鬥成果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 非常努力了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(魯卡崔佛斯中佐)\N入伍當天就被媒體關注
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(超腦力：瞬間移動)\N你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,魯卡崔佛斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,七劍星六等勳章的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,出現在此的怪異\N殺了兩名怪伐軍士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我勸你們最好別看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,遺體缺少頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因為 怪異會吃人腦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,吃人腦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,此時的我們 還不了解許多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原以為怪異 只是如災害般的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 被怪異威脅的日常生活背後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有著極大的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真正該被消滅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是這個瘋狂的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至 我最不解的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,無須被命運所指使
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,相信定會被改寫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們今後 繼續做著夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,朝陽正光輝燦爛 隨後落下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在世界的盡頭 究竟等著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,未來 燈火永恆不滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,誰在威脅我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,誰為我們決定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這是屬於我們的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,未來 你心中的燈火永恆不滅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,結人 入伍當天就表現活躍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,寫報告書有得你受了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他雖然這麼說\N但聽說原本罰得更慘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 該怎麼說你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 第一天的戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,算是合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(緋紅守護者)
